WEBVTT

00:00.240 --> 00:02.400
Viva!

00:02.400 --> 00:06.120
Amanhã terei meu primeiro encontro com o Takeshi-san desde que voltei da América.

00:06.300 --> 00:07.300
Eu estou tão animada.

00:07.610 --> 00:08.570
O que devo vestir?

00:09.630 --> 00:15.130
É melhor eu não usar nada muito chamativo, ou haverá mais rumores sobre mim.

00:17.610 --> 00:22.470
I haven't bought clothes in a long time... or underwear.

00:23.300 --> 00:26.280
Not that I can even buy clothes at this time of day.

00:28.790 --> 00:31.320
But I can't just buy clothes in the middle of a date, either!

00:32.080 --> 00:34.260
Not in front of Takeshi.

00:34.680 --> 00:37.140
He'll start to think of me as that kind of girl.
